<item>
            <title>[QPIDJMS-419] JMS Session is sometimes not recovered on failover reconnect</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/QPIDJMS-419</link>
                <project id="12314524" key="QPIDJMS">Qpid JMS</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In a very rare race the JMS Session that is newly created at the time of a failover and quick reconnect cycle can be missed when recovering the Connection resources.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
